msgid ""
"The following template defines a 2 node Infinispan cluster communicating via "
"TCP, and discovery done using the http://www.jgroups.org/javadoc/org/jgroups/"
"stack/GossipRouter.html[JGroups gossip router]:"
msgstr ""
